		"_postman_id": "dop-holiday-api-collection",
		"name": "DOP Holiday API - Complete Test Suite",
		"description": "Complete collection for testing Data-Oriented Programming Holiday API\n\n## Features Tested:\n- ‚úÖ Create Fixed Holidays with DOP validation\n- ‚úÖ Retrieve holidays by ID\n- ‚úÖ List all holidays\n- ‚úÖ Test invalid date combinations (31/02, 31/04)\n- ‚úÖ Test recurring holidays (year = null)\n- ‚úÖ Test different locality types (Country, Subdivision, City)\n\n## DOP Principles Demonstrated:\n1. **Model Data Immutably and Transparently** - Records with validation\n2. **Model the Data, the Whole Data, and Nothing but the Data** - Specific fields (day, month, year)\n3. **Make Illegal States Unrepresentable** - Invalid dates rejected\n4. **Separate Operations from Data** - Validation in pure functions",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
